ata-copy/.agents/worktrees/oracle-graalvm-reachability-metadata-issue-7628-library-specific-preparation-preflight/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/2653-9d182639/metadata/org.apache.poi/poi-ooxml/index.json:1) to include the test package used by `condition.typeReached`.\\n\\nVerification with the same GraalVM passed:\\n`./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2`\\n`./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2`\\n`./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.bouncycastle:bcpkix-jdk15on:1.62`\\n\\nI left the unrelated user change in [user-code-filter.json](/home/mihailo/git/graalvm-reachability-metadata-copy/.agents/worktrees/oracle-graalvm-reachability-metadata-issue-7628-library-specific-preparation-preflight/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/2653-9d182639/tests/src/org.apache.poi/poi-ooxml/4.1.2/user-code-filter.json:1) untouched.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_8\",\"type\":\"todo_list\",\"items\":[{\"text\":\"Reproduce the org.apache.poi:poi-ooxml:4.1.2 failure with the required GraalVM\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Patch the poi-ooxml 4.1.2 reachability metadata based on the missing-registration error\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Verify the targeted Gradle test passes with the same GraalVM distribution\",\"completed\":true}]}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":11573962,\"cached_input_tokens\":11381120,\"output_tokens\":35118,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":16564}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
